<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="js" lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta content="width=device-width" name="viewport">
    <title>Add claim: Permanent Impairment | MyService</title>
    <link href="docs/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body class="uikit-body uikit-grid uikit-refactor">
    <noscript>
        <p role="alert">This website needs JavaScript to work properly.</p>
    </noscript>
    <nav class="uikit-skip-link">
        <a class="uikit-skip-link__link" href="#main-content">Skip to main content</a>
    </nav>
    <% include ../../../global/partials/header-topbar.ejs %>
        <% include ../../../global/partials/header-claims.ejs %>
            <% include ../partials/help-button.ejs %>
                <main id="main-content">
                    <div class="section-feature border-bottom--mild">
                        <div class="container">
                            <h1 class="margin-below--none margin-above--none">
                                <span class="heading">Recreational activities</span>
                            </h1>
                            <p class="margin-above--mid margin-below--none text-fullwidth">This section is about the phsycological and physical impact your conditions have on your ability
                                to participate in your recreational activities.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="container">
                        <div class="container margin-above">
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-9">

                                    <h3>Complete the statement below
                                        <span class="hint display-block">Answer based on your worst day.</span>
                                    </h3>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-sm-12 margin-below--extra action-group">
                                    <label for="mobility" class="mys-label-nl">The affect my conditions have on my ability to participate in recreational activities
                                        is &nbsp;</label>
                                    <span class="mys-dropdown mys-dropdown-nl">
                                        <select class="uikit-text-input mys-dropdown__select" id="mobility" name="mobility">
                                            <option value="">Choose an option</option>
                                            <option value="minimal">minimal</option>
                                            <option value="low">low</option>
                                            <option value="mild">mild</option>
                                            <option value="moderate">moderate</option>
                                            <option value="high">high</option>
                                            <option value="veryhigh">very high</option>
                                            <option value="extreme">extreme</option>
                                        </select>
                                    </span>

                                    <div class="action-group__reveal--closed" id="mobility-minimal">
                                        <div class="uikit-page-alerts uikit-page-alerts--info">
                                            <p>A
                                                <b>minimal</b> effect is a minor impact on your ability to participate in recreational
                                                activities. The effects are at irregular intervals and between these times
                                                there are no restrictions.
                                                <br>
                                                <i>For example, occasional moments of pain or panic attacks.</i>
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="action-group__reveal--closed" id="mobility-low">
                                        <div class="uikit-page-alerts uikit-page-alerts--info">
                                            <p>A
                                                <b>low</b> effect is a slight impact on your ability to participate in recreational
                                                activities.
                                                <br>
                                                <i>For example, regular moments of pain or discomfort, restriction of some movements
                                                    but still able to continue with the activity.
                                                </i>
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="action-group__reveal--closed" id="mobility-mild">
                                        <div class="uikit-page-alerts uikit-page-alerts--info">
                                            <p>A
                                                <b>mild</b> effect is a small impact on your ability to participate in recreational
                                                activities.
                                                <br>
                                                <i>For example, you have trouble running like you used to but can still go on
                                                    long hikes.
                                                </i>
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="action-group__reveal--closed" id="mobility-moderate">
                                        <div class="uikit-page-alerts uikit-page-alerts--info">
                                            <p>A
                                                <b>moderate</b> effect is a considerable reduction in your ability to participate
                                                in recreational activities. You find strenious activities difficult but less
                                                physical activities are possible.
                                                <i>For example, you can no longer participate in your usual activities and need
                                                    to find alternative options.</i>
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="action-group__reveal--closed" id="mobility-high">
                                        <div class="uikit-page-alerts uikit-page-alerts--info">
                                            <p>A
                                                <b>high</b> effect is a major reduction in your ability to participate in recreational
                                                activities.
                                                <br>
                                                <i>For example, you find it difficult to enjoy simple activities, due to pain,
                                                    discomfort or restrictions in your mobility.</i>
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="action-group__reveal--closed" id="mobility-veryhigh">
                                        <div class="uikit-page-alerts uikit-page-alerts--info">
                                            <p>A
                                                <b>very high</b> effect is a severe reduction in your ability to participate
                                                in recreational activities.
                                                <br>
                                                <i>For example, you are restricted to watching TV or reading. You are unable
                                                    to participate in most activities.</i>
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="action-group__reveal--closed" id="mobility-extreme">
                                        <div class="uikit-page-alerts uikit-page-alerts--info">
                                            <p>An
                                                <b>extreme</b> effect means you are unable to participate in any recreational
                                                activities.
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <% include ../partials/pi-claim4-toggles.ejs %>

                                <div class="row border-top--mild">
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 margin-above">
                                        <fieldset>
                                            <div class="form-group">
                                                <h3 class="uikit-text-input__label" for="textArea">Tell us more
                                                    <span class="hint display-block">This will help us understand how your conditions have affected your ability
                                                        to participate in activities.
                                                    </span>
                                                </h3>
                                                <textarea id="textArea" name="statementText" rows="6"></textarea>
                                            </div>
                                        </fieldset>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="pagination">
                            <button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary" onclick="window.location.href = '/pi-lsq-claim3'">Previous</button>
                            <div class="floated">
                                <button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary" onclick="window.location.href = '/claims'">Save and exit</button>&nbsp;
                                <button class="uikit-btn btnNext" id="btnNext" onclick="window.location.href = '/pi-lsq-claim5'">Save and next</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <% include ../partials/cancel-modal.ejs %>
                    </div>

                </main>

                <% include ../../../global/partials/footer.ejs %>
                    <% include ../partials/panel-help.ejs %>

                        <script>
                            // Dynamic content for mobility rating drop-down
                            $("#mobility").change(function () {
                                // minimal
                                if ($('#mobility :selected').val() == "minimal") {
                                    $("#mobility-minimal").removeClass('action-group__reveal--closed');
                                    $("#mobility-minimal").addClass('action-group__reveal--open');
                                } else {
                                    $("#mobility-minimal").removeClass('action-group__reveal--open');
                                    $("#mobility-minimal").addClass('action-group__reveal--closed');
                                }
                                // low
                                if ($('#mobility :selected').val() == "low") {
                                    $("#mobility-low").removeClass('action-group__reveal--closed');
                                    $("#mobility-low").addClass('action-group__reveal--open');
                                } else {
                                    $("#mobility-low").removeClass('action-group__reveal--open');
                                    $("#mobility-low").addClass('action-group__reveal--closed');
                                }
                                // mild
                                if ($('#mobility :selected').val() == "mild") {
                                    $("#mobility-mild").removeClass('action-group__reveal--closed');
                                    $("#mobility-mild").addClass('action-group__reveal--open');
                                } else {
                                    $("#mobility-mild").removeClass('action-group__reveal--open');
                                    $("#mobility-mild").addClass('action-group__reveal--closed');
                                }
                                // moderate
                                if ($('#mobility :selected').val() == "moderate") {
                                    $("#mobility-moderate").removeClass('action-group__reveal--closed');
                                    $("#mobility-moderate").addClass('action-group__reveal--open');
                                } else {
                                    $("#mobility-moderate").removeClass('action-group__reveal--open');
                                    $("#mobility-moderate").addClass('action-group__reveal--closed');
                                }
                                // high
                                if ($('#mobility :selected').val() == "high") {
                                    $("#mobility-high").removeClass('action-group__reveal--closed');
                                    $("#mobility-high").addClass('action-group__reveal--open');
                                } else {
                                    $("#mobility-high").removeClass('action-group__reveal--open');
                                    $("#mobility-high").addClass('action-group__reveal--closed');
                                }
                                // very high
                                if ($('#mobility :selected').val() == "veryhigh") {
                                    $("#mobility-veryhigh").removeClass('action-group__reveal--closed');
                                    $("#mobility-veryhigh").addClass('action-group__reveal--open');
                                } else {
                                    $("#mobility-veryhigh").removeClass('action-group__reveal--open');
                                    $("#mobility-veryhigh").addClass('action-group__reveal--closed');
                                }
                                // extreme
                                if ($('#mobility :selected').val() == "extreme") {
                                    $("#mobility-extreme").removeClass('action-group__reveal--closed');
                                    $("#mobility-extreme").addClass('action-group__reveal--open');
                                } else {
                                    $("#mobility-extreme").removeClass('action-group__reveal--open');
                                    $("#mobility-extreme").addClass('action-group__reveal--closed');
                                }
                            });

                        </script>

</body>

</html>